627
00:19:26,350 --> 00:19:27,610
Everyone else is good.

628
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:28,830
They are all better than me.

629
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:29,890
Only I am terrible.

630
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:32,470
You misunderstood.

631
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:35,030
I mean,

632
