663
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,170
Did you marry a woman?

664
00:20:19,340 --> 00:20:20,430
Did you marry a woman?

665
00:20:20,430 --> 00:20:22,760
You married a free nanny.

666
00:20:23,390 --> 00:20:24,470
Do I deserve it?

667
00:20:24,470 --> 00:20:25,110
Is this how I

668
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:26,630
should be serving you all?

669
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:29,750
You're really calculating.

670
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,870
We are a family.

671
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:32,150
What kind of calculating is this?

672
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:33,440
What do you mean by family?

673
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,550
What do you mean by family?

674
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:35,430
Did your mom speak anything to me

675
00:20:35,430 --> 00:20:36,630
