676
00:20:36,630 --> 00:20:37,640
Not a word.

677
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:38,270
When did she treat me

678
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:39,960
like family?

679
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:42,550
Can we not quarrel during the Chinese New Year?

680
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:43,190
Our son

681
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,160
