682
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,350
Don't call him our son.

683
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:46,040
That's your son.

684
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,070
Not my son.

685
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:48,160
What did you say?

686
00:20:56,850 --> 00:20:57,650
Min.

687
00:20:59,190 --> 00:20:59,750
Tao.

688
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:03,870
Min.

689
00:21:04,670 --> 00:21:05,780
How could she say that about you?

690
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:07,110
She's in menopause.

691
00:21:07,150 --> 00:21:07,990
It's cold outside.

692
00:21:07,990 --> 00:21:09,230
Let's talk at home.

693
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:10,030
Why should I go home?

694
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,180
To watch them fight

695
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:11,790
