697
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:14,110
I think Aunt Yue

698
00:21:14,130 --> 00:21:15,730
didn't mean that.

699
00:21:15,760 --> 00:21:16,360
Brother,

700
00:21:17,100 --> 00:21:18,870
stop acting foolish.

701
00:21:18,890 --> 00:21:20,480
That's what she meant.

702
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,150
Don't you know what's going on between them

703
00:21:22,150 --> 00:21:23,350
all these years?

704
00:21:23,380 --> 00:21:25,460
Let's not shout on the street

705
00:21:25,490 --> 00:21:27,090
during the Chinese New Year.

706
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:28,630
I don't care.

707
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:29,670
Am I still afraid that

708
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:30,780
If I shout here,

709
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,230
others will mock me?

710
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:33,070
By the time I jumped into the river,

711
00:21:33,070 --> 00:21:34,030
