713
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,400
When did you jump into the river?

714
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,530
I...

715
00:21:39,560 --> 00:21:40,970
I was just trying to scare them.

716
00:21:40,970 --> 00:21:41,850
It was not real.

717
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:43,830
Why didn't anyone

718
