719
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:50,230
Xiaowa.

720
00:21:51,030 --> 00:21:52,360
Happy Chinese New Year.

721
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:53,750
Happy Chinese New Year.

722
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:58,470
You scared me.

