750
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:38,950
Thank you.

751
00:22:38,950 --> 00:22:39,590
Thank you, Si.

752
00:22:39,590 --> 00:22:40,470
No worries. It's not expensive.

753
00:22:40,470 --> 00:22:40,990
Come on.

