799
00:24:22,020 --> 00:24:22,680
Well,

800
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,800
my parents.

801
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:25,970
I'm not bragging.

802
00:24:26,190 --> 00:24:26,790
Both of them

803
00:24:26,790 --> 00:24:28,080
have been together for decades.

804
00:24:28,080 --> 00:24:29,480
They are so close.

805
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:31,020
Even now,

806
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:32,150
they're still romantic

807
00:24:32,150 --> 00:24:33,100
like young people like us.

808
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:34,270
