815
00:24:41,470 --> 00:24:42,660
You dared to smoke behind my back.

816
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:43,590
I'm telling you,

817
00:24:43,710 --> 00:24:45,330
if we can get along, let's still be together;

818
00:24:45,330 --> 00:24:47,190
if we can't, then let's separate.

819
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:49,220
Fang.

820
00:24:49,860 --> 00:24:51,190
