834
00:25:06,310 --> 00:25:07,350
He insisted on

835
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:08,190
carrying all those things by himself,

836
00:25:08,190 --> 00:25:09,510
treating me like a child,

837
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:11,110
and even bought me tanghulu.

838
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:12,680
Where is the tanghulu?

839
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,500
Did you lose it?

840
00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:14,310
Let it be.

841
00:25:14,710 --> 00:25:15,390
Look at this hand.

842
00:25:15,390 --> 00:25:16,390
Look at this hand.

843
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,870
His hand is so numb that he can't move it.

844
00:25:17,870 --> 00:25:19,670
