845
00:25:19,690 --> 00:25:22,150
-Let me blow it for you.
-They're very close.

846
00:25:23,850 --> 00:25:24,770
Blow it.

847
00:25:32,710 --> 00:25:33,660
Fang.

848
00:25:33,690 --> 00:25:35,090
You must be upset

849
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:36,580
