854
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:45,070
Baoshan tried to buy it for me,

855
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:45,830
but he couldn't get any.

856
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:46,640
Exactly.

857
00:25:46,670 --> 00:25:48,070
Baoshan spent the night there

858
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,470
