00:25:51,230 --> 00:25:51,830
If I had known,

861
00:25:51,830 --> 00:25:53,700
I definitely wouldn't have let him go.

862
00:25:53,700 --> 00:25:54,350
A man

863
00:25:54,350 --> 00:25:56,030
should do things for the woman he likes.

864
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:56,710
It's his duty.

865
00:25:56,710 --> 00:25:57,270
No.

866
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:58,220
-Come on.
-We...

867
00:25:58,270 --> 00:25:59,930
Have some food while talking.

868
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,510
I'll go clean up in the kitchen.

869
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:04,500
Mom, don't talk too much.

870
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:05,950
Don't scare Fang.

871
00:26:07,430 --> 00:26:09,030
So diligent. He's a good man.

872
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:12,160
Aunt, we're not in that relationship.

873
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,120
Sooner or later.

874
00:26:13,890 --> 00:26:16,010
You two are destined to be together.

875
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,280
Look at you.

876
00:26:18,190 --> 00:26:19,790
You achieved success at a young age,

877
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:21,980
while he flourished later in life.

878
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,660
You are a match made in heaven.

879
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:24,480
Really?

880
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:27,120
Yes, don't be fooled

881
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:28,300
by our Baoyu's carefree attitude.

882
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:30,630
He's kind and smart.

883
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:32,390
He just hasn't hit the right timing.

884
00:26:32,390 --> 00:26:33,340
Yes, he said it himself.

885
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:34,910
He's just like a tiger that has fallen to the plains.

886
00:26:34,910 --> 00:26:36,030
He was bragging.

887
00:26:36,030 --> 00:26:37,030
He's not much better

888
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:38,920
than the wild dogs in the village.

889
00:26:40,990 --> 00:26:41,990
I can't praise him

890
00:26:41,990 --> 00:26:43,090
just because he's my son.

891
00:26:43,090 --> 00:26:44,240
When it comes to marriage,

892
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,880
it mainly depends on the person

893
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,750
and whether they have a good heart.

894
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:49,080
This is very important.

895
00:26:49,190 --> 00:26:49,900
Yes.

896
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,390
Well,

897
00:26:51,410 --> 00:26:53,160
how to find a good person?

898
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,830
When you look at someone,

899
00:26:54,830 --> 00:26:56,750
you have to consider their family.

900
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:57,790
If a man

901
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:59,000
is unmanly at home,

902
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:01,110
he can still work hard outside

903
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,810
and people will praise him

904
00:27:03,670 --> 00:27:05,600
for treating his wife well at home.

905
00:27:05,670 --> 00:27:06,590
If a woman can't hold her own

906
00:27:06,590 --> 00:27:07,550
at home,

907
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,410
then it's over.

908
00:27:08,570 --> 00:27:10,310
Not only will outsiders look down on her,

909
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,950
but if the wife isn't feeling well,

910
00:27:11,950 --> 00:27:14,160
the whole family won't feel comfortable.

911
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,400
You're right.

912
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,910
My mom's in charge of my family.

913
00:27:16,910 --> 00:27:18,230
My family is fine,

914
00:27:18,330 --> 00:27:19,490
but not my aunt.

915
00:27:19,550 --> 00:27:20,590
She's always suffering

916
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:21,830
and keeps fighting.

917
00:27:21,860 --> 00:27:22,990
Right?

918
00:27:23,050 --> 00:27:24,570
Isn't that proof?

919
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:25,200
Yes.

920
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:27,080
So, in living your life,

921
00:27:27,090 --> 00:27:27,870
you should find a man

922
00:27:27,870 --> 00:27:29,680
who has a sense of responsibility.

923
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:31,000
A responsible man

924
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:31,760
can make the days

925
00:27:31,760 --> 00:27:33,490
without love

926
00:27:33,670 --> 00:27:35,230
rich and fulfilling,

927
00:27:35,330 --> 00:27:37,190
bringing you a sense of security.

928
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,580
Aunt, you're amazing.

929
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:41,480
What you're saying is simple and easy to understand.

930
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:43,390
No wonder Uncle

931
00:27:43,390 --> 00:27:44,650
listens to you so much.

932
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:46,550
I was indeed pretty

933
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:47,870
when I was young.

934
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:49,710
If it weren't for a moment of confusion,

935
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:52,430
I definitely could have married a deputy factory manager.

936
00:27:52,430 --> 00:27:54,070
Auntie, you're so humorous.

937
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:55,990
Do you know how to read faces?

938
00:27:55,990 --> 00:27:56,670
Aunt,

939
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,990
look at my face.

940
00:27:57,990 --> 00:27:58,470
Can my career

941
00:27:58,470 --> 00:28:00,150
advance further?

942
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,560
Of course.

943
00:28:01,940 --> 00:28:02,780
Look at you.

944
00:28:03,050 --> 00:28:04,440
You have a broad forehead

945
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,520
and a rounded lower part.

946
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,780
Especially this nose.

947
00:28:06,890 --> 00:28:08,450
Lucky nose.

948
00:28:09,410 --> 00:28:10,870
What's your position now?

949
00:28:11,010 --> 00:28:12,360
The Director of Teaching and Discipline.

950
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:14,490
Director of Teaching and Discipline?

951
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,370
Alright, within three years,

952
00:28:16,370 --> 00:28:18,100
you will be the vice principal.

953
00:28:19,510 --> 00:28:22,580
[Windward]

954
00:28:21,630 --> 00:28:22,750
Yes.

955
00:28:31,550 --> 00:28:32,150
Old man.

956
00:28:34,040 --> 00:28:34,990
You scared me.

957
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:36,430
Put it out.

958
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:39,240
Did your mom see it?

959
00:28:39,510 --> 00:28:40,110
No.

960
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:41,750
She can't take care of you now.

961
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,870
She was telling Fang that

962
00:28:42,870 --> 00:28:43,590
she could have married the factory manager

963
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:44,630
when she was young,

964
00:28:44,630 --> 00:28:45,350
but ended up marrying you

965
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,350
out of confusion.

966
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,160
Who was confused?

967
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,550
Your mother was confused?

968
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:51,940
I was confused.

969
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,190
Marrying the factory manager?

970
00:28:54,190 --> 00:28:55,230
Was that factory manager crazy

971
00:28:55,230 --> 00:28:56,270
or had water gotten into his brain

972
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:57,400
to dare to marry her?

973
00:28:58,290 --> 00:28:59,500
Let me tell you, son,

974
00:28:59,610 --> 00:29:01,880
I was confused back then

975
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,450
and got tricked by your mom.

976
00:29:03,580 --> 00:29:04,670
She told me

977
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:06,470
she has a fate that brings good fortune to her husband.

978
00:29:06,470 --> 00:29:07,670
Brings good fortune?

979
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,330
What kind of good fortune?

980
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:11,120
I'm about to retire,

981
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:13,320
and I haven't even become a team leader.

982
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:14,830
And she talks about bringing good fortune?

983
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,230
My whole life

984
00:29:17,470 --> 00:29:19,470
has been delayed by her.

985
00:29:19,610 --> 00:29:20,800
Dad, stop smoking.

986
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:21,770
If Mom finds out,

987
00:29:21,780 --> 00:29:23,310
you'll have delayed me too.

988
00:29:32,180 --> 00:29:32,910
Son,

989
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:35,890
I think this chubby girl is pretty good.

990
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:37,920
Can you two make it work?

991
00:29:40,690 --> 00:29:42,000
Dad, I...

992
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,500
To be honest,

993
00:29:44,230 --> 00:29:45,590
at the beginning,

994
00:29:45,990 --> 00:29:47,990
I really didn't want to do anything.

995
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:48,820
But

996
00:29:49,110 --> 00:29:50,550
for some reason,

997
00:29:50,550 --> 00:29:51,870
I don't know why.

998
00:29:51,870 --> 00:29:54,590
Somehow I'm a little panicked.

999
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:56,440
Feeling panicked?

1000
00:29:56,710 --> 00:29:57,480
A little.

1001
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:02,480
The book "Strange Stories from a Chinese Studio" says it well,

1002
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:05,550
"People panic when they meet ghosts."

1003
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,500
Who is the ghost?

1004
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,180
Love.

1005
00:30:14,510 --> 00:30:15,790
Love.

1006
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:18,420
[Carefree]

1007
00:30:21,370 --> 00:30:22,400
Don't prick your fingers.

1008
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,880
How could I possibly prick my fingers after sewing for a lifetime?

1009
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,350
I'm fine. Don't worry.

1010
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:27,110
Grandma.

1011
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:28,740
My grandpa said

1012
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:29,960
he couldn't find his socks.

1013
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,230
Let him barefoot.

1014
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:35,150
Here, your vest is ready.

1015
00:30:35,150 --> 00:30:36,070
Try it on.

1016
00:30:37,050 --> 00:30:38,060
It's quite soft.

1017
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:40,820
It's warm and soft.

1018
00:30:41,300 --> 00:30:41,890
Perfect.

1019
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:44,990
Perfect.

1020
00:30:46,110 --> 00:30:46,830
Didn't you say

1021
00:30:46,830 --> 00:30:48,510
Zi will leave in a few days?

1022
00:30:48,710 --> 00:30:49,500
She just knew how to speak.

1023
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:51,230
Why are you in a hurry to go back?

1024
00:30:51,390 --> 00:30:51,990
Grandma,

1025
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:54,160
she can't live in our house forever.

1026
00:30:54,250 --> 00:30:55,900
Shanqing is worried about causing you trouble.

1027
00:30:55,900 --> 00:30:57,400
What trouble? I'll take care of Zi.

1028
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:57,800
I...

1029
00:30:57,820 --> 00:30:59,390
I'm so willing to do so.

1030
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:00,350
Bring back

1031
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:01,210
what she likes to eat later.

1032
00:31:01,210 --> 00:31:01,810
-Okay.
-Okay.

1033
00:31:01,810 --> 00:31:02,670
Thank you, Grandma.

1034
00:31:02,670 --> 00:31:03,340
Good.

1035
00:31:03,630 --> 00:31:04,150
How is it?

1036
00:31:04,150 --> 00:31:05,020
Great.

1037
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:05,990
Isn't it nice?

1038
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,570
It fits you well.

1039
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:09,050
Grandma,

1040
00:31:10,250 --> 00:31:12,080
you must live a long life.

1041
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,620
When I get married and have kids in the future,

1042
00:31:13,620 --> 00:31:14,590
I need you to help me with babysitting.

1043
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:15,590
Don't worry,

1044
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,750
Grandma will at least live for another 20 years.

1045
00:31:17,750 --> 00:31:18,310
No problem.

1046
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,710
No, make it 40 years.

1047
00:31:19,730 --> 00:31:21,530
Then I'll turn into an old witch.

1048
00:31:23,390 --> 00:31:24,700
Here, this is yours.

1049
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:26,190
-Mine?
-Put it on.

1050
00:31:26,470 --> 00:31:28,300
All right. Yours is done too.

1051
00:31:28,410 --> 00:31:29,790
My little granddaughter,

1052
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:31,430
you look good in anything.

1053
00:31:31,670 --> 00:31:32,670
What do you think?

1054
00:31:32,870 --> 00:31:33,710
This little beauty.

1055
00:31:33,710 --> 00:31:35,530
There's nothing we can do. She's so good-looking.

1056
00:31:35,530 --> 00:31:36,170
Alright,

1057
00:31:36,510 --> 00:31:37,270
Grandma will make one for you

1058
00:31:37,270 --> 00:31:38,790
each year,

1059
00:31:38,910 --> 00:31:40,370
and then I'll feel at ease.

1060
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,070
But looking at so many pieces,

1061
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:43,730
Yaya and I can't wear them all.

1062
00:31:43,950 --> 00:31:46,350
Do you think it's just you and Yaya who will wear them?

1063
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:47,390
There's also your mom.

1064
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:48,690
Your mom is my child too,

1065
00:31:48,690 --> 00:31:49,530
right?

1066
00:31:49,850 --> 00:31:50,890
And your uncle.

1067
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:53,080
Although your uncle is a loser,

1068
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:54,590
you can't dislike him

1069
00:31:54,590 --> 00:31:56,120
just because he's useless.

1070
00:31:56,710 --> 00:31:58,390
This world is so vast.

1071
00:31:58,390 --> 00:32:00,390
There are not many

1072
00:32:00,390 --> 00:32:01,520
successful people.

1073
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:02,470
For ordinary people,

1074
00:32:02,470 --> 00:32:03,380
even if they're not successful,

1075
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:04,820
if they're healthy

1076
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:05,630
and can be good people,

1077
00:32:05,630 --> 00:32:08,160
that's already a blessing for their parents.

1078
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:11,030
Then, Grandma, do you treat my dad

1079
00:32:11,050 --> 00:32:12,310
like a little kid too?

1080
00:32:12,550 --> 00:32:13,990
Of course.

1081
00:32:14,010 --> 00:32:15,280
Since Pengfei married into the family,

1082
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,730
he's been my own son.

1083
00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:18,670
You say, in this lifetime,

1084
00:32:18,670 --> 00:32:20,000
how many people can call me "Mom"

1085
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,200
or call me "Grandma"?

1086
00:32:21,340 --> 00:32:23,100
It's rare and all about fate.

1087
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,200
Even when you're 80,

1088
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:25,660
you're still my children.

1089
00:32:28,190 --> 00:32:28,990
Grandma,

1090
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:29,990
this piece is so small,

1091
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:31,030
I can't wear it.

1092
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,430
You surely can't wear it.

1093
00:32:32,430 --> 00:32:34,030
This is for Zi.

1094
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:36,070
Zi

1095
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:38,390
doesn't have parents or a grandmother.

1096
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,180
You can imagine how much suffering

1097
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:41,710
she has to endure to grow up.

1098
00:32:41,790 --> 00:32:43,470
So I sewed her a little vest

1099
00:32:43,650 --> 00:32:44,850
to let her know

1100
00:32:44,950 --> 00:32:47,880
there are still people who care for her in this world.

1101
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,670
Here, look at these.

1102
00:32:51,950 --> 00:32:53,280
They're all Grandma's,

1103
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:54,580
secretly put in

1104
00:32:54,580 --> 00:32:55,710
for you.

1105
00:32:55,710 --> 00:32:57,210
This is 100 yuan.

1106
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:59,170
This is a sycee.

1107
00:32:59,770 --> 00:33:01,060
This is rice.

1108
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,160
This is a blessing.

1109
00:33:02,210 --> 00:33:03,860
They're all sewed in here.

1110
00:33:03,950 --> 00:33:04,690
I have one too.

1111
00:33:04,690 --> 00:33:06,250
Everyone has one.

1112
00:33:06,390 --> 00:33:07,100
What do you think?

1113
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:08,950
Grandma, you are so nice.

1114
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:11,620
I must live until 100 years old.

1115
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:12,720
A thousand years old.

1116
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,920
A thousand years old.

1117
00:33:14,930 --> 00:33:15,970
You're back!

1118
00:33:16,050 --> 00:33:16,930
Welcome back.

1119
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:18,650
Happy Chinese New Year.

1120
00:33:18,650 --> 00:33:20,250
Happy Chinese New Year.

1121
00:33:55,750 --> 00:33:56,630
Give them to me.

1122
00:34:17,409 --> 00:34:18,219
Tao,

1123
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,409
don't take

1124
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,389
what I said yesterday

1125
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:27,230
personally.

1126
00:34:27,750 --> 00:34:28,870
That's because

1127
00:34:28,870 --> 00:34:30,600
I was quarreling with your dad.

1128
00:34:30,870 --> 00:34:32,110
I didn't mean it.

1129
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:32,750
It's okay.

1130
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:35,719
Min told me

1131
00:34:36,350 --> 00:34:38,150
she almost jumped into the river

1132
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,320
because of your quarrel.

1133
00:34:44,290 --> 00:34:45,679
All these years, you and my dad

1134
00:34:45,679 --> 00:34:47,409
have had a bumpy life together.

1135
00:34:47,580 --> 00:34:49,239
Actually, I know all about it.

1136
00:34:50,750 --> 00:34:51,949
It's been almost four years

1137
00:34:51,949 --> 00:34:53,340
since I left home for school.

1138
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:55,909
I haven't really come back during the winter and summer breaks.

1139
00:34:55,909 --> 00:34:56,989
When I told you

1140
00:34:56,989 --> 00:34:59,790
I had to make up classes or work during my vacation,

1141
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,490
I was actually lying to you.

1142
00:35:03,060 --> 00:35:04,460
I really understand Min.

1143
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,640
This is something I owe her.

